speaker: david_friendly
text: Once upon a time, in Greenland's icy wilds, lived tough seal hunter Kunu. He wore fur from his catches. Harpoon ready, he ruled frozen fjords. He hunted seals by day.

speaker: david_friendly
text: He chilled in igloo with polar bears by night. News hit like bad fart one day. Orange-haired asshole Trump wanted to buy Greenland. Like a goddamn Happy Meal.

speaker: david_friendly
text:
Kunu spat seal jerky and cursed. "That motherfucker thinks he can price my homeland? Fuck that!"
He grabbed harpoon, sharper than Trump's tiny hands. He stormed into blizzard.

speaker: david_friendly
text:
"Bloated balloon bastard, full of hot air and bullshit lies," he grumbled. "Beefing with windmills, calling 'em cancer. I harpoon beasts."
"Pussy-grabbin' ghost, fake tan fraud—fuck him!"

speaker: david_friendly
text: Under northern lights like cosmic middle finger, Kunu pictured confronting Trump's tower. "You buggin' hard, clown-ass prick! |Get clapped by this Inuit blaze!"

speaker: david_friendly
text: Trump was washed-up has-been. He hid in Mar-a-Lago, crying over votes. Polar bears nodded agreement. "No cap, that Trump nigga's empire gonna capsize," Kunu declared.

speaker: david_friendly
text: "MAGA tears freezing, straight L parade. Greenland forever free, you decayed fuck!" Kunu returned to igloo, raging warmly.

speaker: david att
text: Moral: Don't fuck with seal hunter's turf. Or get harpooned in ass. Sweet dreams—sleep before ice melts from hot air. The end.
